prodNameC: 羅氏抗德國麻疹免疫球蛋白G檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Cal1 Negative calibrator 1, 2 bottles of 1.0 mL each:
Human serum, non-reactive for anti-Rubella IgG; preservative.
Cal2 Positive calibrator 2, 2 bottles of 1.0 mL each:
Anti-Rubella IgG approx. 400 IU/mL in human serum; preservative.

Reagent -
M Streptavidin-coated microparticles, 1 bottle, 6.5 mL:
Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL; preservative.
R1 Anti-h IgG-Ab~biotin, 1 bottle, 10 mL:
Biotinylated monoclonal anti-h IgG antibody (mouse), RLP,
phosphate buffer pH 6.8; preservative.
R2 Anti-Rubella-Ab-fragment~Ru(bpy)2+3, recombinant E1~biotin, recombinant E1~Ru (bpy)2+3, 1 bottle, 10 mL:Ruthenylated monoclonal anti-Rubella antibody fragment,
biotinylated recombinant E1, ruthenylated recombinant E1,
phosphate buffer pH 6.8; preservative.

PreciControl
？PC RUBIGG1: 8 bottles, each containing 1.0 mL of control serum
Human serum, negative to low positive for Rubella IgG antibodies
(approx. 4 IU/mL); preservative.
？PC RUBIGG2: 8 bottles, each containing 1.0 mL of control serum
Human serum, positive for anti-Rubella IgG antibodies
(approx. 75 IU/mL); preservative.
